<br>
<br>
Picked up some new songs today at highkeep. Plan to use them soon.<br>
<br>
Plan a trip to the Estate of the Unrest, to pick up a Dark Boned Bracelet.<br>
<br>
Ran as fast as I can to spires... (Note to Self: don't fall of cliff next time)<br>
Play my mandolin and heal up....<br>
<br>
Continue running to spires.. <br>
Stop and kill a bear or 2 to get a high quality bear pelt.<br>
Twist &quot;Largo's Melodic Binding&quot; and &quot;Anthem&quot; didn't get a pelt :P<br>
Oh well spires is right there, I'll just jog over, and hitch a <br>
ride to the Nexus and jump to Faydwer. <br>
<br>
&quot;Hail Sc........&quot;, <br>
I hear Bristlebane laughing.<br>
duh.... I'm in Shadowhaven, by the soulbinder, ummmm ok I wanted to be in <br>
this area... but with equipment.. at least she did her job..<br>
(Note to Self: be sure you finish singing &quot;Largo's Melodic Binding&quot;<br>
before talking to Scion)<br>
/sighs heavily.... ok back to Antonica.<br>
<br>
Get my equipment, and wait to go back to the Nexus. <br>
While waiting, someone calls for help, I help kill the beetles, and <br>
save the person. (Hey I remembered not to sing &quot;Largo's&quot;), <br>
Wait.... duh.. spires take forever... <br>
<br>
A druid asks, &quot;If I need a lift to the moon?&quot; <br>
I say, &quot;What I really want to get to is the Estate of Unrest.&quot; <br>
She said, &quot;That she can take me to Faydwer&quot;<br>
<br>
Wow thats great... saves me some time. <br>
I asked, &quot;What I can do to repay her.&quot;<br>
She says, &quot;There is no need since I helped a friend of hers.&quot;<br>
<br>
Ahhh heck... a good deed does get repayed, I smile and go for a ride.<br>
<br>
ok, off to the Estates, pick up a cleric who was going that way,<br>
<br>
Ran into some Agua Goblins.. Bah I hate being rooted... ohh poison.. even better.<br>
duh.. heal up and travel some more.. finally get the estates.. <br>
<br>
See if anyone wants to join in the campaign, against the undead.. a Necro, <br>
and druid.. mmm I think.. not sure.. actually can't remember the classes..<br>
ok.. Cleric says lets go through back door and camp in there. fine..<br>
This place is new to me, I figure thats the way to do it, just wanted to get<br>
that bracelet, figure sooner or later I'll get the chance... <br>
<br>
Ack!! train of undeads,  try to draw them to me and save cleric.. blah...<br>
no luck.. run... cleric dies.. *sniff*  shortly there after I hear Bristlebane<br>
laughing again, he must be enjoying my antics, because he keeps on bringing me <br>
back. <br>
<br>
Ok different attack, I'll just wait until someone tells me the bracelet has dropped<br>
or I get into a bigger group.  I hang around for a bit scaring the trains away<br>
with my fearful voice, gee even skellies run away when I sing, go figure.<br>
<br>
Someone tells me that there is a bracelet on the stairway to the basement, I go<br>
through the front door, not nowing the layout quite yet, 2 skellies attack and<br>
a mummy, ( I want my mommy now)  debate about using my fearful voice, I tried but<br>
my voice cracks a few times.. and I get stunned a few times.. time to get the heck<br>
out.<br>
<br>
Darn, now where did the front door go, I hear Bristlebane chuckling again, ahh found<br>
the door. I get out... seems like all the undead hate me now, gee it must be my voice.<br>
<br>
I run to the safe spot, and the undead stop chasing me, I think I have enough<br>
for one day. Time to camp, and re-evaluate in the morning.<br>
<br>
  <br>
Tsol Ylenasni of 27 Songs<br>
